  "reference_number": "RUS0705",
  "remarks": "\nKonstantin KNYRIK (hereafter referred to as KNYRIK) is the co-founder of Newsfront. Newsfront is a Russian news organisation known for publishing disinformation about the war against Ukraine, thus supporting and promoting actions which destabilise Ukraine. As a Director, co-founder, and contributor to Newsfront, KNYRIK is both engaging in, supporting and promoting policies and/or actions which destabilise Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
